org.wonderly.jini.serviceui
Class ServiceUIFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.wonderly.jini.serviceui.ServiceUIFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdminUIJFrameFactory, PropertyAdminUIJFrameFactory
public abstract class ServiceUIFactory
extends Object

This is a base class for all ServiceUI Factories. It implements methods for all Swing related component retrievals. The subclass can declare the needed Factory interfaces to attach those factories to the implementation. The subclass can then implement buildJComponent to build the needed component that will be encapsulated by all the other container types.

Subclasses can also override the methods here to add toolbar or menu components to the toplevel containers if needed.

Author:
Gregg Wonderly - gregg.wonderly@pobox.com
